long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Show precise search volume, CPC, and competition data for any keyword. The data is sourced from Google Keyword Planner.

Google Keyword Planner has always been a free and powerful tool provided by Google official, especially for those involved in SEO, PPC advertising, and keyword research. 

However, for those who have not advertised on Google, the Google Keyword Planner will not display accurate keyword search volume. Instead, it will only show a search range, such as 10K to 100K.

All the data of keywords was sourced from Google Keyword Planner API, so it's reliable.

The two main feature of Google Keyword Planner Enhancer is:
1.Display the search volume of search keywords below the search box in Google Search.
2.Replace the search volume range in Google Keyword Planner with precise numerical values.

All data is obtained in real-time from Google, so all the data is up-to-date.
